channel.title: Cant query data from a google sheets source
channel.description:
I dont get any error but there is no output data.
Its a sheet with more than 20000 rows. Is there a limit to the size of the google sheets?
i followed these instructions https://redash.io/help/data-sources/querying/google-sheets

item.title: Cant query data from a google sheets source
item.dc:creator: jesse
item.description:
Are you able to see any data from a smaller sheet? I’m not aware of a size limit. It’s possible the entire connection is faulty, though.
